nto her back so he could look into her face. "I''ll be happy to show you several times a day.', 35879, 0), (196662, 'All I know is that I like how I feel when I''m with you. I love how protective you are and that you aren''t afraid to say you''re sorry. I like how you touch me and kiss me. I like how you hold me, but more than anything, I like the possibilities that are before us.""We''re in the middle of a war," he warned. She shrugged and ran her hands up his chest and over his shoulders to clasp around his neck. "Every couple has their own issues to get through.', 35879, 0), (196663, 'Yes, Daisy. Feel it,” he murmured against her mouth. “Feel what’s in my heart for you.” His hand slipped under the covers...', 34735, 0), (196664, 'Seeing that glorious body and to-die-for face only made her crave him more.	Then he had kissed her.	And what a kiss!	It was a kiss like none other. There was fire and a hunger that was both savage as well as tender.	At first.	Then the fire had come. The kiss had charred her, searing her from the inside out. Each touch of his tongue, each time those lips of his moved over here, had been the most incredible feeling in the world.', 35879, 0), (196665, 'Jack explained. “Daisy, you were meant for me. Dane destroyed that. You’re lucky I don’t set you on fire right this minute. It’s either you or him. Pick.” Jack chewed on a toothpick, took it out of his mouth and pointed it at her and then Dane. “Pick, pick, pick,” he said, pointing back and forth.', 34735, 0), (196666, 'Your death, strange human. I mean, your injury. No murder, just a little maiming. So I can leave. Maiming’s not so bad.', 23990, 0), (196667, 'But worries are for people who can’t pull grown men apart with their bare hands.', 23990, 0), (196668, 'I eye the three of them, considering. They’ll need a lesson in discretion before I go. Not a lethal lesson. Mom wouldn’t like that.', 23990, 0), (196669, 'My teeth rip skin; my jaws snap bones. I am fast, lightning-fast, snuff— oh-was